dvd -love comes softly `` oh my goodness ! ! ! '' if you love a feel good , emotional roll-a-coaster , family movie . this is it ! ! this is one of the best movies i have ever watched . it has all the elements of every emotion you can come up with . the actors are superb and you feel like your part of the scene . i have watched it 3 times and will watch it again . just make sure you have a box of kleenex handy